    "Foundational studies by 62 have proven the efficiency of quantization techniques and combined gradient computation in considerably reducing memory usage during training 63.",
    "Building upon these contributions, the latest innovations have introduced hierarchical memory management systems that enable dynamic memory allocation and sparse gradient updates, thereby further optimizing memory utilization, as highlighted by 64.",
